s some special\nfeatures of the radiative decays $\\mu \\to e \\gamma$ and ${\\bar B}\\to X_s\n\\gamma$. Future experiments, especially those concerned with lepton flavor\nviolation, should see deviations from SM predictions unless one of the MNSUSY\nvariants with enhanced flavor symmetries is realized.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Sep 2014 14:21:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Oct 2014 14:02:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Feb 2015 07:26:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-24"}
